com.adobe.cq.dam.cfm

Enum SyncStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SyncStatus>
      • com.adobe.cq.dam.cfm.SyncStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SyncStatus>

    public enum SyncStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<SyncStatus>
    Enumeration that defines the synchronization state of a "slave" variation against the respective element master.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      BOTH_CHANGED
      Both master and "slave" have been changed since last sync ("conflict" state)
      IN_SYNC
      Master and "slave" are synchronized - they each share the same content state (this could mean both have the same content, or the slave has a "processed" content directly derived from master's current content)
      MASTER_CHANGED
      Master has changed since last synchronization
      UNSYNCED
      Master and "slave" are not synchronized at all
      VARIATION_CHANGED
      "Slave" has changed since last synchronization
